attributes.review:
It took literal DAYS to download, and when I finally tried opening the app, all it did was crash and make horrific scraping and screeching noises in the voice of a man who has killed hundreds of thousands 🟠🍊🥕. When I looked back at the app, my eyes gazed upon an image of the man behind the slaughter of thousands of innocent Americans, and I felt my soul leave my body✨👁👄👁✨. I began to panic, (like I did when my right to healthcare was removed 🧚‍♀️🏳️‍🌈✨💙💖🤍💖💙) and was filled with fear. All of a sudden, I saw a bright, calming white light up ahead as I gently floated through the void. As I came nearer, I heard a loud voice speak the language of the gods, and say “Be Not Afraid!✨💕💖”. The majestic form of JOE BIDEN materialized right front of me, and gazed into my eyes. While he was doing so, I noticed that another ethereal figure appeared next to him. It was OBAMA!!! 🥺😭☺️However, I was despairing😭, because I only knew his first name, and never his last. I simply knew him as “OBAMA”. The two figures spoke to me at once, and gave me this message: “Xue🌸Hua💗Piao✨Piao🌱, Bei🏳️‍🌈Feng🧚‍♀️Xiao🌿Xiao🌼. ✨💖Make America Great Again 💕🌷✨🌱By Voting Trump Out Of Office🧚‍♀️🌼☺️”. In that moment, I knew what I had to do. JOE BIDEN and OBAMA gave the strength💪and courage🙌to make the journey back to the realm of the living. When I awoke back in my physical body, I snapped my phone in half, bought a new one (orange 🍊🟠🥕 free), and wrote this review. I am currently in the process of sageing 🌙✨⭐️my house. DO NOT GET THIS APP!! 

(But what do I know, since I “”don’t deserve rights”” 😭😭💕🧚‍♀️✨🌱)
